@resource(aws.route53.Zone, HostedZone)
Name {domain_name}

@resource(aws.route53.Record, AppAlbRecord)
In $HostedZone
Name: app.{domain_name}
Type: A
Alias has "name" and "zone_id" of $ServerAlb, and "evaluate_target_health" set to True

@resource(aws.route53.Record, CertificateValidationRecord)
In $HostedZone
The name, type and records are derived from the $ServerCertificate domain validation option.
Ttl: 300